@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rnssgt(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (v0 + (1.00 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.05)))
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.37 + v1 + 0.55)) + (wp.sin(tmp + 0.21) / wp.cos(v2 + 0.54)))
    tmp = wp.sin(((v2 + 0.14 * v2 + 0.90) + (v0 + 0.49 + v1 + 0.77)))
    v0 = ((0.14 + wp.cos(v0 + 0.94)) + wp.abs((tmp + 0.50 * tmp + 0.50)))
    data[tid] = v0
